The hilarious illustration created by Raphaela Wilson depicts a chocolate covered banana wearing sunglasses and sprinkled with nuts, awaiting his partner to surprise her. On the floor is the cat , unamused and laying underneath the thrown banana peel. The funny quote bubble reads: "Didn’t you say to try something new?" while the inside greetings are: "You drive me bananas in all the good ways. Happy Valentine’s Day!" These clever words can be personalized to your heart’s desire. If you have a great sense of humor and love silly, naughty humor, these funny banana Valentine’s day cards are sure to get a laugh, enjoy!
